{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Hi everyone."},{"time":2000,"text":"I'm an artist and a dad -- second time around."},{"time":5000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":7000,"text":"And I want to share with you my latest art project."},{"time":10000,"text":"It's a children's book for the iPad."},{"time":13000,"text":"It's a little quirky and silly."},{"time":15000,"text":"It's called \"Pop-It,\""},{"time":17000,"text":"And it's about the things little kids do with their parents."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"So this is about potty training --"},{"time":24000,"text":"as most of you, I hope, know."},{"time":27000,"text":"You can tickle the rug."},{"time":29000,"text":"You can make the baby poop."},{"time":31000,"text":"You can do all those fun things."},{"time":35000,"text":"You can burst bubbles."},{"time":39000,"text":"You can draw, as everyone should."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43000,"text":"But you know, I have a problem with children's books:"},{"time":45000,"text":"I think they're full of propaganda."},{"time":47000,"text":"At least an Indian trying to get one of these American books in Park Slope, forget it."},{"time":50000,"text":"It's not the way I was brought up."},{"time":53000,"text":"So I said, \"I'm going to counter this with my own propaganda.\""},{"time":55000,"text":"If you notice carefully,"},{"time":57000,"text":"it's a homosexual couple bringing up a child."},{"time":60000,"text":"You don't like it?"},{"time":62000,"text":"Shake it, and you have a lesbian couple."},{"time":65000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":67000,"text":"Shake it, and you have a heterosexual couple."},{"time":71000,"text":"You know, I don't even believe in the concept of an ideal family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"I have to tell you about my childhood."},{"time":76000,"text":"I went to this very proper Christian school"},{"time":79000,"text":"taught by nuns, fathers, brothers, sisters."},{"time":82000,"text":"Basically, I was brought up to be a good Samaritan,"},{"time":84000,"text":"and I am."},{"time":86000,"text":"And I'd go at the end of the day to a traditional Hindu house,"},{"time":89000,"text":"which was probably the only Hindu house"},{"time":91000,"text":"in a predominantly Islamic neighborhood."},{"time":95000,"text":"Basically, I celebrated every religious function."},{"time":98000,"text":"In fact, when there was a wedding in our neighborhood,"},{"time":101000,"text":"all of us would paint our houses for the wedding."},{"time":103000,"text":"I remember we cried profusely"},{"time":105000,"text":"when the little goats we played with in the summer"},{"time":107000,"text":"became biriani."},{"time":109000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":111000,"text":"We all had to fast during Ramadan."},{"time":113000,"text":"It was a very beautiful time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"But I must say,"},{"time":117000,"text":"I'll never forget, when I was 13 years old, this happened."},{"time":120000,"text":"Babri Masjid --"},{"time":122000,"text":"one of the most beautiful mosques in India,"},{"time":124000,"text":"built by King Babur, I think, in the 16th century --"},{"time":127000,"text":"was demolished by Hindu activists."},{"time":129000,"text":"This caused major riots in my city."},{"time":131000,"text":"And for the first time,"},{"time":133000,"text":"I was affected"},{"time":135000,"text":"by this communal unrest."},{"time":137000,"text":"My little five-year-old kid neighbor"},{"time":139000,"text":"comes running in,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and he says, \"Rags, Rags."},{"time":144000,"text":"You know the Hindus are killing us Muslims. Be careful.\""},{"time":147000,"text":"I'm like, \"Dude, I'm Hindu.\""},{"time":149000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":150000,"text":"He's like, \"Huh!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"You know, my work is inspired"},{"time":156000,"text":"by events such as this."},{"time":158000,"text":"Even in my gallery shows,"},{"time":160000,"text":"I try and revisit historic events"},{"time":162000,"text":"like Babri Masjid,"},{"time":164000,"text":"distill only its emotional residue"},{"time":166000,"text":"and image my own life."},{"time":168000,"text":"Imagine history being taught differently."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"Remember that children's book"},{"time":171000,"text":"where you shake and the sexuality of the parents change?"},{"time":174000,"text":"I have another idea."},{"time":175000,"text":"It's a children's book about Indian independence --"},{"time":178000,"text":"very patriotic."},{"time":180000,"text":"But when you shake it, you get Pakistan's perspective."},{"time":182000,"text":"Shake it again, and you get the British perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":185000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"You have to separate fact from bias, right."},{"time":192000,"text":"Even my books on children"},{"time":194000,"text":"have cute, fuzzy animals."},{"time":196000,"text":"But they're playing geopolitics."},{"time":198000,"text":"They're playing out Israel-Palestine,"},{"time":200000,"text":"India-Pakistan."},{"time":202000,"text":"You know, I'm making a very important argument."},{"time":204000,"text":"And my argument [is]"},{"time":206000,"text":"that the only way for us to teach creativity"},{"time":210000,"text":"is by teaching children perspectives"},{"time":212000,"text":"at the earliest stage."},{"time":214000,"text":"After all, children's books are manuals on parenting,"},{"time":216000,"text":"so you better give them children's books that teach them perspectives."},{"time":219000,"text":"And conversely,"},{"time":221000,"text":"only when you teach perspectives"},{"time":223000,"text":"will a child be able to imagine"},{"time":225000,"text":"and put themselves in the shoes"},{"time":227000,"text":"of someone who is different from them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229000,"text":"I'm making an argument that art and creativity"},{"time":231000,"text":"are very essential tools in empathy."},{"time":234000,"text":"You know, I can't promise my child"},{"time":236000,"text":"a life without bias --"},{"time":238000,"text":"we're all biased --"},{"time":240000,"text":"but I promise to bias my child with multiple perspectives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}